column4: RT @Georgetown Ijeoma (G’19) worked with @GUProvostOffice and Student Affairs to create the (In)Visibility at Georgetown: Past, Present, & Future exhibit, which features art from Hoyas across campus. The exhibit will open on April 12 in the Healey Family Student Center: https://t.co/g08axl7RoD
